text: A by-election was held in the New South Wales state electoral district of Monaro on 23 November 1918. The by-election was triggered by the death of Gus Miller (). ==Result== Gus Miller () died. ==See also== *Electoral results for the district of Monaro *List of New South Wales state by-elections ==Notes== ==References== Category:New South Wales state by-elections Category:1918 elections in Australia Category:1910s in New South Wales
title: 1918 Monaro state by-election
